parameters: So this is the Caledony Magic Academy...

Finally arrived, huh? And man, what a huge
building.

Of course. It's a school where magic users from
all over the world gather.
So this is the Caledony Magic Academy...

Finally arrived, huh? And by the way, what a huge
building.

Of course. It's a school where magicians from all
over the world gather, after all.

(I feel like I've seen this scene before... No,
maybe it's just my imagination.)

[Masamune] Permission has been granted. If you
become the vice president, you can stay until
graduation.

[Masamune] You must really want information about
Caledonia.

[Masamune] But I'm glad. While you're here, there
shouldn't be any investigations from the Samuel
Church.
[Olivia] Now I can graduate with peace of mind.

[Hiyo] If Masamune becomes the vice president, it
seems like he could create new rules.

[Hiyo] Olivia, the vice president, didn't create
much.
[Masamune] I guess it's fine for now.

[Hiyo] Oh no, like for example, implementing a
class for practicing baby-making.

[Masamune] Please spare me... I mean, it's Hiyo
for now.

[Hiyo] I will properly accompany Masamune-kun, you
know.

[Masamune] (Sigh... It seems like it's going to be
a noisy day from now on.)

[Hiyo] The student council room is the love nest
of Masamune-kun and me, isn't it?

[Olivia] Make sure to invite the new students,
okay?

[Olivia] I wonder if I should come and visit
occasionally even after graduation.

[Hiyo] Please stop acting like a nasty old man,
okay?

Here... it seems like we can spend our time
laughing until graduation.
